  <brief_title>Non-Contrast Magnetic Resonance Angiography Assessment of Patients Referred for Transcatheter Aortic Valve Implantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Can Non-Contrast Magnetic Resonance Angiography Accurately Define Arterial Access and Aortic Root Anatomy in Patients Referred for Transcatheter Aortic Valve Implantation?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>University of Michigan</agency>
